Package: scPAS
Type: Package
Title: A tool for identifying phenotype-associated single-cell subpopulations by integrating bulk and single-cell sequencing data (scPheno)
Version: 0.2.0
Author: c(person("Aimin", "Xie", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "aiminyy1993@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Aimin Xie <aiminyy1993@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 4.0.5)
Description: scPAS is a novel approach that utilizes the bulk phenotypes, such as disease stage, tumor metastasis, treatment response, and survival outcomes, to identify the most highly phenotype-associated cell subpopulations from single-cell data.
Imports: Rcpp, Matrix, Seurat, preprocessCore, survival
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
